# Most trivial case: single H atom

prtvol -2

acell 3*10
diemac 1.0d0
diemix 1.0d0
ecut 5
intxc 1
kptopt 0
kpt 3*0
natom 1
nband 1
nkpt 1
nline 3
nstep 20
nsym 1
ntypat 1
rprim  1 0 0
       0 1 0
       0 0 1
tolwfr 1.0d-14
typat 1
xred 3*0
wtk 1
znucl 1


